-- 
2011-07-08T10:04:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/u-s-stock-futures-decline-amid-renewed-concern-over-european-debt-crisis.html
U.S. stock-index futures fell as
bonds of  Europe ’s weakest economies declined amid renewed
concern about the region’s debt crisis.  Futures on the Standard & Poor’s 500 Index expiring in
September dropped 0.2 percent to 1,348.6 at 11:02 a.m. in
